  <entry>
    <title>静下来，听听社会底层的声音</title>
    <link href="https://shanshatest.github.io/posts/27671/"/>
    <id>https://shanshatest.github.io/posts/27671/</id>
    <published>2020-12-19T02:33:27.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-12-19T02:33:27.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#前言"></a> 前言</h2><blockquote><p>非常高兴团队成员殃雾在制作该视频的过程中邀请我提供建议。</p></blockquote><p>我个人是没有看过小丑这部电影的，但是通过殃雾这短短几分钟的剪辑，从事情的起端，发展，高潮，结局，让我对小丑这个角色以及电影想表达的观点有了一个初步了解。</p><p>下面就由咕咕咕的我来给观看过亦或是没有观看过的朋友们，谈谈殃雾的第一部影视剪辑。</p><h3 id="视频原链接-哔哩哔哩独播"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#视频原链接-哔哩哔哩独播"></a> <a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1o54115771">视频原链接 哔哩哔哩独播</a></h3><hr /><h1 id="正文"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#正文"></a> 正文</h1><h2 id="起承转合"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#起承转合"></a> 起承转合</h2><h3 id="起-introduce-as-joker"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#起-introduce-as-joker"></a> 起: Introduce as Joker</h3><p>作为一部剪辑的开头部分，如何使得未看过该电影的人有一个初步印象，或是说使得看过的观众能重温剧情，便是剪辑能否吸引观众的关键所在。</p><blockquote><p>画面从“Sometimes I can’t feel the world”引入，同时伴有耳鸣的音效</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/1.jpg" alt="" /><br /><strong>这是以悲伤的画面，将抑郁感逐渐拉深</strong></p><blockquote><p>紧接着，是几秒的心理咨询对话</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/2.jpg" alt="" /></p><p><strong>arthur在与心理医生的对话里，可以看到他并不能被医生所重视，医生对想他一样的病人，似乎总是那一套说辞</strong></p><p><strong>无奈的笑 谁又能真正去关心他这样的人?</strong></p><h3 id="承-family-makes-him-arthur"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#承-family-makes-him-arthur"></a> 承: Family makes him Arthur</h3><p>此时承接开头部分低沉的气氛，母亲与“家人”，可能是他生活中的一线光明，背景音乐改变，偏向轻松与欢快</p><blockquote><p>画面呈现黑色，并附有各种叫他“Arthur”的声音。从黑色的画面结束，有从黑暗中唤醒他的意义，因为好像，有人在乎他。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/3.jpg" alt="" /></p><blockquote><p>此时整体画面开始偏向明亮，但始终蒙着一层黄色的灰尘</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/4.jpg" alt="" /></p><blockquote><p>片中提到，Arthur的母亲对他的引导。保持微笑，挂着笑脸。为传递欢笑而存活于世。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/5.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/6.jpg" alt="" /></p><blockquote><p>在这时，转到另一幅画面。母亲深信韦恩会帮助他们，Arthur似乎也相信，他们将会有过上正常生活。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/7.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/8.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/9.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/10.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/11.jpg" alt="" /></p><blockquote><ul><li>如果他看见这个破屋，他会恶心</li><li>他可是托马斯韦恩</li><li>因为托马斯韦恩是一个好人</li><li>我为他们家工作了这么多年</li><li>至少他会回信的</li></ul></blockquote><p><strong>然而这一切都是幻想······</strong></p><h3 id="转-but-wayne-is-part-of-lies"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#转-but-wayne-is-part-of-lies"></a> 转: But Wayne is part of lies</h3><p>从这一部分开始，内容即将达到高潮。所以，各种矛盾将在此埋下伏笔，因为这一切都是谎言，背景音乐的节奏加快，试图表现Arthur难以接受的痛苦。</p><blockquote><p>韦恩的冷漠，Arthur逐渐得知真相，众多的信息涌向Arthur，成为压垮他精神的最后一棵稻草</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/12.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/13.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/14.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/15.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/16.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/17.jpg" alt="" /></p><blockquote><p>他笑韦恩他们这些资本家，他们高傲，自私自利。他笑自己，曾经对丑陋的资本家抱有幻想。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/18.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/19.jpg" alt="" /></p><h3 id="合-welcome-to-jokers-party"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#合-welcome-to-jokers-party"></a> 合: Welcome to Jokers’ party</h3><p>前面埋下的诸多伏笔都将在此时爆发的展现出来</p><blockquote><p>Arthur杀死母亲，这是Arthur从一个精神病人黑化的开始</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/20.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/21.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/22.jpg" alt="" /></p><blockquote><p>Arthur在节目里的发言，他对社会的理解，正是反映了社会底层与那些高高在上的资本家的冲突。</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/23.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/24.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/25.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/26.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/27.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/28.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/29.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/30.jpg" alt="" /></p><blockquote><p>通过集中展现Arthur遭遇的不公，与Arthur黑化后的报复，将整个剪辑推向高潮</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/31.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/32.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/33.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/34.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/35.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/36.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/37.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/38.jpg" alt="" /></p><blockquote><p>Arthur领导Jokers暴动，让他这虚幻而不真实的一生，开始受到关注</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/39.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/40.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/41.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/42.jpg" alt="" /><br /><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/Joker/43.jpg" alt="" /></p><hr /><h3 id="写在片尾"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#写在片尾"></a> 写在片尾</h3><p>因为是通过剪辑来了解小丑这部电影，可能关于剧情的理解并不到位，还请多多谅解。<br />欢迎在评论区提出宝贵建议</p><hr /><h2 id="友情链接"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#友情链接"></a> 友情链接</h2><blockquote><p><a href="https://sakurasep.top/">上杉九月的博客</a><br /><a href="https://sakurasep.club/">团队首页</a></p></blockquote><hr /><p><img src="https://gitee.com/sakurasep/pictures/raw/master/chevereto/%E6%88%90%E5%93%814.png" alt="" /></p>]]></content>
    
    
